text: Laramie is a city in the U.S. state of Wyoming. It is the county seat of Albany County. The University of Wyoming is located in Laramie. == Recent history == In 1998, Matthew Shepard was murdered in this town. == References == == Other websites == * *City of Laramie, official website Category:Cities in Wyoming Category:County seats in Wyoming Category:Albany County, Wyoming
